{
  "name": "ELC — 01 Hot Lead Alert",
  "active": false,
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1",
    "timezone": "Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh"
  },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔥 Hot Lead Alert\nFastAPI gọi webhook này khi có booking mới.\n\n**Cần cấu hình (n8n → Settings → Variables/Env):**\n- `ELC_API_URL` = https://api.eurowindowlightcity.net\n- `INTERNAL_WEBHOOK_TOKEN` = trùng env backend\n- `MANAGER_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID` = chat_id manager/admin\n- Credential **Telegram** = bot token từ @BotFather\n\nGợi ý nút bấm: thêm Inline Keyboard trong node Telegram nếu muốn (xem docs/n8n-setup.md).",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 380
      },
      "id": "note-1",
      "name": "Hướng dẫn",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-40, -40]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "hot-lead-alert",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-1",
      "name": "Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [400, 200],
      "webhookId": "hot-lead-alert"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "chatId": "={{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.sale_telegram_chat_id }}",
        "text": "=🔥 *HOT LEAD MỚI — 30 GIÂY ĐỂ PHẢN HỒI*\n\n👤 *Khách:* {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_name }}\n📞 {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_phone }}\n🏠 *Căn:* {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.unit_id }} — {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.unit_summary }}\n🕐 *Hẹn:* {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.booking_time }}\n⭐ *AI score:* {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.ai_score }}/100\n\n📝 {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.ai_summary }}\n\n👉 [Mở Chatwoot trả lời ngay]({{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.conversation_url }})",
        "additionalFields": {
          "appendAttribution": false,
          "parse_mode": "Markdown"
        }
      },
      "id": "tg-notify",
      "name": "Telegram — Báo Sale",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.telegram",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [640, 200],
      "credentials": {
        "telegramApi": {
          "id": "REPLACE_TELEGRAM_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "ELC Sale Bot"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "amount": 5,
        "unit": "minutes"
      },
      "id": "wait-5m",
      "name": "Chờ 5 phút",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [880, 200],
      "webhookId": "wait-hot-lead"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "={{ $env.ELC_API_URL }}/leads/{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_id }}/contacted_at",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "X-Internal-Token",
              "value": "={{ $env.INTERNAL_WEBHOOK_TOKEN }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "http-check",
      "name": "Check contacted_at",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1120, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "typeValidation": "loose",
            "version": 2
          },
          "combinator": "and",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-uncontacted",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.contacted_at }}",
              "rightValue": "",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "empty",
                "singleValue": true
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "if-uncontacted",
      "name": "Sale chưa phản hồi?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1360, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "chatId": "={{ $env.MANAGER_TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID }}",
        "text": "=⚠️ *CẢNH BÁO: SALE CHƯA PHẢN HỒI HOT LEAD*\n\nSale *{{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.sale_name }}* chưa liên hệ sau 5 phút.\n\n👤 Khách: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_name }} — {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_phone }}\n🏠 Căn: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.unit_id }}\n⭐ AI score: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.ai_score }}/100\n\n👉 [Mở Chatwoot]({{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.conversation_url }})",
        "additionalFields": {
          "appendAttribution": false,
          "parse_mode": "Markdown"
        }
      },
      "id": "tg-escalate",
      "name": "Telegram — Escalate Manager",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.telegram",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [1620, 120],
      "credentials": {
        "telegramApi": {
          "id": "REPLACE_TELEGRAM_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "ELC Sale Bot"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "no-reply@eurowindowlightcity.net",
        "toEmail": "={{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.sale_email }}",
        "subject": "=[HOT LEAD] {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_name }} — phản hồi ngay",
        "emailFormat": "text",
        "text": "=Bạn có hot lead chưa phản hồi:\n\nKhách: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_name }} - {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.lead_phone }}\nCăn: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.unit_id }} - {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.unit_summary }}\nHẹn: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.booking_time }}\n\nMở Chatwoot: {{ $('Webhook').item.json.body.conversation_url }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "email-backup",
      "name": "Email backup (bật khi Telegram lỗi)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [1620, 320],
      "disabled": true
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Webhook": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Telegram — Báo Sale",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Telegram — Báo Sale": {
